<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN">
<html lang="zh-Hant-TW">
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=big5" http-equiv="content-type">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>校園景點介紹</title>
    <style>
    body {
          font-family: "微軟正黑體", sans-serif;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          background-image: url('../icon/Bg%20summer.jpg');
          background-size: cover;
          background-position: center;
          background-repeat: no-repeat;
          background-attachment: fixed;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          min-height: 100vh;
        }
    header {
      background-color: #3f51b5;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .spot {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 800px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .spot img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    .spot h2 {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #eee;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>校園景點介紹</header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="spot"> <img src="../pic/B1%281%29.jpg" alt="體育館">
        <h2>體育館 ─ 見證汗水與榮耀的殿堂</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="spot"> <img src="../pic/c2.jpg" alt="學生活動走廊">
        <h2>學生活動走廊 ─ 創意與童趣的展示牆</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="spot"> <img src="../pic/C2%281%29.jpg" alt="教學大樓">
        <h2>教學大樓 ─ 我們每日求知的地方</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="spot"> <img src="../pic/g2.jpg" alt="校門口">
        <h2>校門口 ─ 每日進出的起點與終點</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="spot"> <img src="../pic/L1.jpg" alt="圖書館">
        <h2>圖書館 ─ 知識與想像力的寶庫</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer>製作：702 團隊｜探索我們熟悉的校園每一角<br>
      <a href="../../../index.html"><img style="width: 161px; height: 88px;"

          alt="" src="../icon/back%20home%20summer.png"></a><br>
      <a href="../school%20life/school%20life.html"><img style="width: 134px; height: 59px;"

          src="../icon/last%20page%20summer.png"></a><a href="../../Autumn/teacher/teacher.html"><img

          style="width: 156px; height: 53px;" src="../icon/next%20page%20summer.png"></a><br>
      <a href="../../spring/boys/boys.html"><img style="width: 129px; height: 77px;"

          src="../icon/last%20season%20summer.png"></a><a href="../../Autumn/teacher/teacher.html"><img

          style="width: 129px; height: 76px;" src="../icon/next%20season%20summer.png"></a></footer>
  </body>
</html>
